          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Eligibility and How to Participate</p>",
            "description": "<p><strong>Eligibility:</strong> Open to all users of Yarbo products, specifically those utilizing the <strong>Snow Blower</strong> module.<strong>Submission Content:</strong> Content must focus on Yarbo's \"action/working status\" during winter. Recommended shooting ideas include:</p><ul><li>The moment Yarbo automatically starts (e.g., paired with \"lights turning on\" shots)</li><li>\"Before and After\" shots: Snow-covered driveway → Cleaned completion</li><li>Time-lapse footage showcasing the entire snow removal process<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Minimum Submission Requirements (Threshold for Review):</strong><em>Video:</em></p><ul><li>Duration: ≥ 30 seconds</li><li>Quality: ≥ 720p (1080p+ recommended)</li><li>Content: Must include shots of Yarbo in \"action/working status\" such as operating, driving, or changing modules</li><li>Stability: Avoid obvious shaking<br/></li></ul><p><em>Photo:</em></p><ul><li>Quantity: ≥ 5 images</li><li>Content: Must include Yarbo interacting with people/pets or clear before-and-after scenes</li><li>Clarity: High resolution, good composition<br/></li></ul><p><strong>How to Submit:</strong> Participants must submit their content through the <strong>official website</strong>. Submission via social media is optional.</p><ul><li><strong>Social Media:</strong> Post on Instagram, Facebook, YouTube, or TikTok<br/>Use the Hashtag: <strong>#MyYarboJourney</strong><br/>Tag the official Yarbo account: <strong>@Yarbo</strong></li><li><strong>Official Website:</strong> Visit the dedicated event page and submit the form, which requires:<br/>Name/Email<br/>Region (for the Yarbo snow-clearing map)<br/>Uploading the submission (video or image)<br/>Social media post link</li></ul>"
          }
        },
