            "description": "<p><strong>Prizes:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Third Place:</strong> $50 USD Gift Card/person (Total 200 winners)</li><li><strong>Second Place:</strong> $500 USD Gift Card/person (Total 10 winners)</li><li><strong>First Place:</strong> $1,000 USD Gift Card/person (Total 5 winners)</li><li>Note: Prizes will be awarded to the top submissions based on quality, creativity, and public voting. The number of winners for each prize tier will correspond to the actual number of qualifying top submissions.<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Selection & Voting:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Review:</strong> The team will select high-quality content for the online gallery</li><li><strong>Public Voting:</strong> Voting begins once submission is successfully uploaded to the website. Each person can cast one vote per day</li><li><strong>Final Decision:</strong> Winners determined based on content quality, creativity, and public voting results<br/></li></ul>"
